channel.title: Forum of Lies 17 - Unseen and Warlock Victory!
channel.description:
## [color=orange]Welcome to Forum of Lies 17![/color] <small>Hosted by @Marluxion and @Livicus</small>
### [color=orange]Rules[/color]
https://forum.imperium42.com/t/forum-of-lies-official-hub/1515
### [color=orange]Gameplay [/color] Days will be 3 IRL days long, or shorter if someone is executed. Nights will be 1 IRL day long Actions are done by messaging me in your rolecard Unseen/Cult will talk through a special forum dm Priest will speak with the dead through a special forum dm All classes will be used, and will be used as they are found in the [Class Cards Thread](https://forum.imperium42.com/t/fol-class-cards-now-officially-official/1998/) When you receive a card you will have 24 hours to reply, confirming you have received it
### [color=orange]Executions [/color] To accuse someone say "**/accuse [player]**" or "**/vote [player]**" When majority is reached on a player, a trial will begin. Trials will last for 12 hours unless The King uses Decide Fate. Executions end the Day
### [color=orange]Journals [/color] Message me your entire journal, the last draft I receive before you die shall be the one displayed
### [color=orange]To Join[/color] To join, simply express interest in joining by saying something like "I want to join" or "/join" or "/in" or "sign me up, coach" or whatever you want
# [color=orange]Players: [/color] 1. [color=red]**PoisonedSquid**[/color]- [color=steblue]**The Knight**[/color] - **Died Night 3** 2. [color=red]**Luxy**[/color] - [color=purple]**The Poacher**[/color] - **Died Night 3** 3. [color=red]**Alice**[/color] - [color=steblue]**The Physician**[/color] - **Died Night 2** 4. [color=red]**Marcus**[/color]- [color=steblue]**The Sheriff**[/color] - **Executed Day 3** 5. [color=red]**Insanity**[/color] - [color=cyan]**The Warlock**[/color] - **Executed Day 2** 6. **Bazinga** 7. **Hjasik** 8. **Firekitten** 9. [color=red]**Mercenary**[/color] - [color=steblue]**The Chronomancer**[/color] - **Died Night 1** 10. [color=red]**Captain**[/color]- [color=steblue]**The Butler**[/color] - **Died Night 3** 11. **Sam17z** 12. **Boopydoop** 13. [color=red]**WazzaAzza :crown:** [/color] - - [color=steblue]**The Good King**[/color] - **Died Night 3** 14. [color=red]**Margaret**[/color] - [color=steblue]**The Sheriff**[/color] - **Died Night 3** 15. [color=red]**Kai_5**[/color] - [color=steblue]**The Butler**[/color] - **Died Night 3** 16. [color=red]**Isaac_Gonzalez**[/color] - [color=steblue]**The Drunk**[/color] - **Died Night 3**
Spectators: Ashe
